CLI tool usage:

Usage: dgg [OPTION...] file
  -v  --version   Version information
  -h  --help      Help contents
  -a  --adapter   (required) Adapter name. E.g.: EMGM
  -d  --datatype  (optional) Specify datatype for which to derive. Generates
                             for all datatypes if left blank.
  -o  --output    (optional) Output file. E.g.: Instances.hs

